Export a Workload History

To export a workload history:

Required Editions: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited
User Permissions: Workforce Engagement Analyst

Before exporting, apply filters (9 options) to the workload history.
The export can't exceed 40,000 records. Filter data further if necessary.

Open Intelligent Forecasts from the App Launcher.
Click to open a workload history.
Click Export.
Click Export to confirm.
The CSV file downloads to your default downloads folder.
